headline: Costco's menu adds an iconic treat that McDonald's used to offer
summary: When I’m shopping at Costco, I tend to want to get in and out of the store as quickly as possible. That’s because I have very little patience for large crowds, which Costco tends to attract. headline: A Look at McDonald's (MCD) Valuation Following a 5% Dividend Increase
summary: McDonald's (MCD) just gave investors something to consider, announcing a 5% increase in its quarterly dividend. This move highlights management's steady confidence in the fast-food giant’s ability to deliver reliable profits. See our latest analysis for McDonald's. McDonald's share price showed steady momentum over the past year, with a 6.94% total shareholder return and resilient performance despite some volatility in the broader fast-food sector.
